Package octoshape.osa2.listeners

Interface Summary
MultiStreamInfoListener Listens for multistream and basestream information from a StreamPlayer.
OctoshapeSystemListener Listens for information from the OctoshapeSystem class.
ProblemListener Listener for Problems from StreamPlayer or OctoshapeSystem.
ProgressListener Listens for indications of how far we are progressed with something.
PushStatusListener Callback for status message from a StreamPusher.
StatusChangedListener Listens for StreamPlayer status changes.
StreamConfigurationListener Listens for information on how the stream is configured in the Octoshape system.
StreamInfoListener Listens for stream source information from a StreamPlayer.
StreamSignalListener A listener for Octoshape stream signals.
TimeInfoListener Listener for time information from the Octoshape client.
UMetaDataListener Listener for Octoshape u-meta data in the current stream.
